<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-8264] Problems with multicolumn relations and COMPACT STORAGE</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-8264</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As discovered in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7859&quot; title=&quot;Extend freezing to collections&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-7859&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-7859&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, there are a few issues with multi-column relations and &lt;tt&gt;COMPACT STORAGE&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The first issue is that IN clauses on multiple columns aren&apos;t handled correctly.  There appear to be other issues as well, but I haven&apos;t been able to dig into them yet.  To reproduce the issues, run each of the tests in &lt;tt&gt;MultiColumnRelationTest&lt;/tt&gt; with a &lt;tt&gt;COMPACT STORAGE&lt;/tt&gt; version of the table.  (Changing the tests to do that automatically will be part of the ticket.)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
