                            <comment id="14212584" author="thobbs" created="Fri, 14 Nov 2014 18:29:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached 2.0 patch backports the fix from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7859&quot; title=&quot;Extend freezing to collections&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-7859&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-7859&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, fixes exclusive slice restriction filtering for non-composite comparators, and updates the MultiColumnRestrictionTests to cover compact storage.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The 2.1 patch does the same, with the exception of the &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7859&quot; title=&quot;Extend freezing to collections&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-7859&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-7859&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
